    {
      "name": "Socket.IO Events Guide",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Socket.IO Connection Guide",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{socket_url}}",
              "host": ["{{socket_url}}"]
            },
            "description": "# Socket.IO Events Guide\n\n## Connection\n```javascript\nconst socket = io('http://localhost:3006', {\n  auth: {\n    token: 'YOUR_JWT_TOKEN'\n  }\n});\n```\n\n## Events to Emit (Client → Server)\n\n### 1. join_conversation\n```javascript\nsocket.emit('join_conversation', {\n  conversation_id: 1\n});\n```\n\n### 2. send_message\n```javascript\nsocket.emit('send_message', {\n  conversation_id: 1,\n  message: 'Hello!',\n  message_type: 'text' // text, image, file, voice\n});\n```\n\n### 3. typing_start\n```javascript\nsocket.emit('typing_start', {\n  conversation_id: 1\n});\n```\n\n### 4. typing_stop\n```javascript\nsocket.emit('typing_stop', {\n  conversation_id: 1\n});\n```\n\n### 5. mark_as_read\n```javascript\nsocket.emit('mark_as_read', {\n  conversation_id: 1,\n  message_id: 123\n});\n```\n\n### 6. leave_conversation\n```javascript\nsocket.emit('leave_conversation', {\n  conversation_id: 1\n});\n```\n\n## Events to Listen (Server → Client)\n\n### 1. new_message\n```javascript\nsocket.on('new_message', (data) => {\n  console.log('New message:', data);\n  // data: { message_id, conversation_id, sender_id, sender_type, message, message_type, created_at }\n});\n```\n\n### 2. user_typing\n```javascript\nsocket.on('user_typing', (data) => {\n  console.log('User typing:', data);\n  // data: { conversation_id, user_id, user_type, user_name }\n});\n```\n\n### 3. user_stopped_typing\n```javascript\nsocket.on('user_stopped_typing', (data) => {\n  console.log('User stopped typing:', data);\n});\n```\n\n### 4. message_read\n```javascript\nsocket.on('message_read', (data) => {\n  console.log('Message read:', data);\n  // data: { conversation_id, message_id, read_by_id, read_by_type }\n});\n```\n\n### 5. error\n```javascript\nsocket.on('error', (error) => {\n  console.error('Socket error:', error);\n});\n```\n\n### 6. connected\n```javascript\nsocket.on('connected', (data) => {\n  console.log('Connected:', data);\n});\n```\n\n## Complete Example\n```javascript\nconst io = require('socket.io-client');\n\nconst socket = io('http://localhost:3006', {\n  auth: { token: 'YOUR_JWT_TOKEN' }\n});\n\nsocket.on('connected', (data) => {\n  console.log('Connected as:', data);\n  \n  // Join conversation\n  socket.emit('join_conversation', { conversation_id: 1 });\n});\n\nsocket.on('new_message', (message) => {\n  console.log('Received:', message);\n});\n\n// Send message\nsocket.emit('send_message', {\n  conversation_id: 1,\n  message: 'Hello from Socket.IO!',\n  message_type: 'text'\n});\n```"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
